souls. So it would take 10 level 50 mobs to make one emerald. Make the method to do this a spell with ~50 mana cost, no recast time but a casting time of 3-6 seconds. Add a level 59AA ability that give you and instant manaless soul stealing ability. Necros might actually use those spells then.</P><P>Arch Lich – Add ultravision and fear immunity<BR>That seems fitting</P><P>Epic:<BR>I really wish I was a good artist because I know exactly how the damn epic should look I just cant express it with a picture. It should be a bare spine curved like a real one with a demonic looking skull on top...or a dragon-ish looking skull. The skull should waver and look around much like the enchanter epic. The eyes should glow green and blood should be seen to drip down the skull/spine. </P><P>The effect should be the level 50+ darkness not the per-50 darkness.</P><P>Philiak Mortus Lv.51 Necromancer of Xev<BR>Zeratis Lv.30 Monkey<BR>Sam: Where should I put this thing so that it doesnt hurt anyone we know or care about?<BR>Max: Out the window Sam. There's nobody but strangers out there.<BR><a href="http://www.pvponline.com" target="_blank">www.pvponline.com</a></font></td>
